panels.title: ai-gateway Service Apdex

targets.expr:
sum(
  label_replace(
    vector(0) and on() (gitlab_service_apdex:ratio_1h{env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"}),
    "period", "na", "", ""
  )
  or
  label_replace(
    vector(1) and on () (gitlab_service_apdex:ratio_5m{env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"} < on(tier, type) group_left() (1 - (14.4 * (1 - slo:min:events:gitlab_service_apdex:ratio{component="",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"})))),
    "period", "5m", "", ""
  )
  or
  label_replace(
    vector(2) and on () (gitlab_service_apdex:ratio_1h{env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"} < on(tier, type) group_left() (1 - (14.4 * (1 - slo:min:events:gitlab_service_apdex:ratio{component="",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"})))),
    "period", "1h", "", ""
  )
  or
  label_replace(
    vector(4) and on () (gitlab_service_apdex:ratio_30m{env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"} < on(tier, type) group_left() (1 - (6 * (1 - slo:min:events:gitlab_service_apdex:ratio{component="",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"})))),
    "period", "30m", "", ""
  )
  or
  label_replace(
    vector(8) and on () (gitlab_service_apdex:ratio_6h{env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"} < on(tier, type) group_left() (1 - (6 * (1 - slo:min:events:gitlab_service_apdex:ratio{component="",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"})))),
    "period", "6h", "", ""
  )
)

panels.description: Apdex is a measure of requests that complete within a tolerable period of time for the service. Higher is better.

seriesOverrides.alias: 6h Degradation SLO (5% of monthly error budget)
1h Outage SLO (2% of monthly error budget)

targets.legendFormat: 6h Degradation SLO (5% of monthly error budget)
1h Outage SLO (2% of monthly error budget)

panels.title: server SLI Apdex

targets.expr:
sum(
  label_replace(
    vector(0) and on() (gitlab_component_apdex:ratio_1h{component="server",env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"}),
    "period", "na", "", ""
  )
  or
  label_replace(
    vector(1) and on () (gitlab_component_apdex:ratio_5m{component="server",env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"} < on(tier, type) group_left() (1 - (14.4 * (1 - slo:min:events:gitlab_service_apdex:ratio{component="server",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"})))),
    "period", "5m", "", ""
  )
  or
  label_replace(
    vector(2) and on () (gitlab_component_apdex:ratio_1h{component="server",env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"} < on(tier, type) group_left() (1 - (14.4 * (1 - slo:min:events:gitlab_service_apdex:ratio{component="server",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"})))),
    "period", "1h", "", ""
  )
  or
  label_replace(
    vector(4) and on () (gitlab_component_apdex:ratio_30m{component="server",env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"} < on(tier, type) group_left() (1 - (6 * (1 - slo:min:events:gitlab_service_apdex:ratio{component="server",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"})))),
    "period", "30m", "", ""
  )
  or
  label_replace(
    vector(8) and on () (gitlab_component_apdex:ratio_6h{component="server",env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"} < on(tier, type) group_left() (1 - (6 * (1 - slo:min:events:gitlab_service_apdex:ratio{component="server",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"})))),
    "period", "6h", "", ""
  )
)

    vector(1) and on() (gitlab_component_errors:ratio_5m{component="waf",env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"} > on(tier, type) group_left() (14.4 * slo:max:events:gitlab_service_errors:ratio{component="waf",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"})),
    "period", "5m", "", ""
  )
  or
  label_replace(
    vector(2) and on() (gitlab_component_errors:ratio_1h{component="waf",env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"} > on(tier, type) group_left() (14.4 * slo:max:events:gitlab_service_errors:ratio{component="waf",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"})),
    "period", "1h", "", ""
  )
  or
  label_replace(
    vector(4) and on() (gitlab_component_errors:ratio_30m{component="waf",env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"} > on(tier, type) group_left() (6 * slo:max:events:gitlab_service_errors:ratio{component="waf",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"})),
    "period", "30m", "", ""
  )
  or
  label_replace(
    vector(8) and on() (gitlab_component_errors:ratio_6h{component="waf",env="$environment",environment="$environment",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"} > on(tier, type) group_left() (6 * slo:max:events:gitlab_service_errors:ratio{component="waf",monitor="global",type="ai-gateway"})),
    "period", "6h", "", ""
  )
)

panels.description:
GCP Quota utilization / limit ratio

Saturation on a quota may cause problems with creating infrastructure resources on GCP.

To fix, we can request a quota increase for the specific resource to the GCP support team.
 Lower is better.

targets.expr:
clamp_min(
  clamp_max(
    max by(environment, tier, type, stage, shard, project, metric, quotaregion) (
  clamp_min(
    clamp_max(
      (
        gcp_quota_usage{env="$environment",environment="$environment",type="ai-gateway"}
      /
        gcp_quota_limit{env="$environment",environment="$environment",type="ai-gateway"}
      ) > 0
      ,
      1)
  ,
  0)
)

  ,1)
,0)
